r495 | jblang | 2010-06-27 00:09:21 +0200 (Sun, 27 Jun 2010) | 1 line

Add void **data parameter to alloc_image function so that pointer to platform-dependent image object can be stored in image struct.  This will allow use of platform-specific text and drawing libraries.
